om/~vladimir/demos/photos.svg\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG photo demo</a> (Visuelle Effekte und Interaktion)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://starkravingfinkle.org/projects/demo/svg-bubblemenu-in-html.xml\" rel=\" noopener\">Bubblemenu</a> (Visuelle Effekte und Interaktion)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://starkravingfinkle.org/blog/2007/07/firefox-3-svg-foreignobject/\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML transformationen</a>&nbsp;using <code>foreignObject</code> (Visuelle Effekte and transforms)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://svg-whiz.com/svg/linguistics/theCreepyMouth.svg\" rel=\" noopener\">Phonetics Guide</a> (Interaktiv)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.lutanho.net/svgvml3d/platonic.html\" rel=\" noopener\">3D objects demo</a> (Interaktiv)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.themaninblue.com/experiment/Blobular/\" rel=\" noopener\">Blobular</a> (Interaktiv)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/video.svg\" rel=\" noopener\">Video embedded in SVG</a> (oder benutze den <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/video_svg.tar.bz2\" rel=\" noopener\">lokalen Download</a>)</li>\n <li><a href=\"http://summerstyle.github.io/summer/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Summer HTML image map creator</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/summerstyle/summer\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source code</a>)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"video","title":"Video","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test1.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Streaming Anime, Movie Trailer and Interview</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test2.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Billy's Browser Firefox Flick</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test3.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Virtual Barber Shop</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=